# Variables
#@baseServer = https://rutzsco-agent-mcp-server-hub-app.agreeablepond-d8205ba9.eastus2.azurecontainerapps.io/
@baseServer = https://localhost:7077
@apiKey = dev-api-key-12345


### Health check (no API key required)
GET {{baseServer}}/api/healthz

### Time - Get current time (remote)
GET {{baseServer}}/api/time
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Weather - Forecast by coordinates (remote)
GET {{baseServer}}/api/weather/forecast?lat=38.8894&lon=-77.0352
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### YouTube - Download to MP3 (remote) - defaults (16kHz mono, 64kbps)
POST {{baseServer}}/api/youtube/mp3
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"
}

### YouTube - Download to MP3 (local) - custom options
POST https://localhost:5000/api/youtube/mp3
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "outputPath": "output_audio_16khz_mono.mp3",
  "sampleRateHz": 16000,
  "channels": 1,
  "bitrateKbps": 64
}

### Negative test - Missing API key should return 401
GET {{baseServer}}/api/time
Accept: application/json
